WEBVTT

1
00:14:01.190 --> 00:14:04.860 
只要你发誓 再也不伤害梅丽珊卓夫人
If you swear never to raise your hand to the Lady Melisandre again.

2
00:14:04.900 --> 00:14:08.060 
我发誓
I swear it.

3
00:14:08.100 --> 00:14:10.370 
但我无法承诺不出言反对她
I can't swear never to speak against her.

4
00:14:10.400 --> 00:14:12.430 
你就那么不在乎自己的性命
You have little regard for your own life.

5
00:14:12.470 --> 00:14:14.540 
确实 陛下
Quite little, Your Grace.

6
00:14:14.570 --> 00:14:16.940 
完全不在乎
Verging on none.

7
00:14:16.970 --> 00:14:20.780 
您本可以昨天或是明天释放我
You could have freed me yesterday or tomorrow,

8
00:14:20.810 --> 00:14:23.450 
但是您偏偏现在来 赶在那孩子命丧利刃前
but you came to me now before this boy is put to the knife

9
00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:27.280 
因为您知道我会劝您三思而行
because you knew I'd counsel restraint.

10
00:14:28.850 --> 00:14:31.620 
您到这里来听我说 因为您自己心里也是这样认为的
You came to hear me say it because you believe it yourself.

